  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a rectangular circuit with a battery and four resistors. The left vertical branch has resistor R sub 1 and the right vertical branch has the battery.  From top to bottom, the middle vertical branch has resistor R sub 2, after which the branch splits into two inner vertical branches. The left inner vertical branch has resistor R sub 3. The right inner vertical branch has resistor R sub 4. The two inner vertical branches merge again into the middle vertical branch.\" src=\"/images/6730193a56260c942a0696aa72dd1f50.svg\"></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">In the circuit diagram shown in the figure, the four resistors are all identical. Which of the following claims about a current in the circuit is true?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i4",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The current in Resistor <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"R sub 1\"><math alttext=\"R sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mtext>R</mtext><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> is less than half the current in the battery.</p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The current in Resistor <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"R sub 2\"><math alttext=\"R sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mtext>R</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span> is half the current in the battery.</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The current in resistors <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"R sub 2\"><math alttext=\"R sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mtext>R</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span>, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"R sub 3\"><math alttext=\"R sub 3\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mtext>R</mtext><mn>3</mn></msub></math></span></span>, and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"R sub 4\"><math alttext=\"R sub 4\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mtext>R</mtext><mn>4</mn></msub></math></span></span> are equal to each other.</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The current in Resistor <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"R sub 3\"><math alttext=\"R sub 3\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mtext>R</mtext><mn>3</mn></msub></math></span></span> Resistor <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"R sub 4\"><math alttext=\"R sub 4\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mtext>R</mtext><mn>4</mn></msub></math></span></span> are equal to each other.</p>",
